page.title: 19CHANGES IN EMSWORTH
page.content: We found by interviewing people, a lot of changes had taken place in { {Emsworth}during the past sixty years. We interviewed a man who had been living in{Emsworth}for fifty seven years.He spoke about one of the changes he had noted. He told us that there used to be a log factory at the bottom of{Stanley Road} but there are new houses. We interviewed another man in{Emsworth who had lived there for forty four years.This is one of the changes he had noted. He talked about an old oyster vessel in the harbour,which now has been removed so that it is safer for boats. We also interviewed a lady from{ {Emsworth}who had been living there for forty seven years.She said that where {Lillywhites}is there used to be a row of houses.
